[I] COSMIC Store

[T] COSMIC Store supports system packages via PackageKit, support for
[T] installing media codecs on the host, managing system and user flatpak
[T] repositories, supports system and user flatpak repositories, installing
[T] COSMIC applets, and a dedicated category for "Made for COSMIC" apps.

[U] https://github.com/pop-os/cosmic-store/

[A] System76 <info@system76.com>
[M] NoTag <notag@t2sde.org>

[C] extra/tool
[F] CROSS

[E] add flatpak

[L] GPL3
[V] 1.0.10

[CV-GROUP] cosmic-desktop
[D] a965665015d9d354ac38d3374d0f5f10bca99bce1e4fb685f01afe1a cosmic-store-epoch-1.0.10.tar.gz https://github.com/pop-os/cosmic-store/archive/epoch-1.0.10/

